Installation instructions for Disposition 0.8

First:
	make

Second (as root):
	make install

Which makes a copy of the program "disp" in the directory /usr/local/bin.

If you want to uninstall the program, run (as root):
	make uninstall

To install the library and the header files, run (as root):
	make install-dev

Which makes a copy of the header files in the directory /usr/local/include
and a copy of the library file in the directory /usr/local/lib.

If you want to uninstall the library, run (as root):
	make uninstall-dev

